      <title>Version 0.5.66</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <style>
          body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 12px; }
          h2 { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 12px 0; }
          h3, h4 { font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 6px 0; }
          li { margin: 4px 0; }
          ul { padding-left: 20px; }
          .source { margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 8px; font-size: 11px; }
          @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body { color: #e0e0e0; background: #1a1a1a; }
            h2, h3, h4 { color: #fff; }
            .source { border-top: 1px solid #333; color: #888; }
            a { color: #58a6ff; }
          }
          @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
            body { color: #333; background: #fff; }
            h2, h3, h4 { color: #111; }
            .source { border-top: 1px solid #ddd; color: #999; }
            a { color: #0366d6; }
          }
        </style>
        <h2>What's New in 0.5.66</h2>
        <h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed excessive diagnostic logging that could slow down performance during normal use in Ableton and other DAWs</li>
          <li>Eliminated false "bug detected" warnings that were incorrectly triggered during polyphonic MIDI playback (playing chords)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="source">Build 1126 &middot; <a href="https://github.com/danielraffel/PlunderTube/commit/7c46399f">7c46399f</a> on main</p>
      ]]></description>
